MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: Mapping to load data from the BI EXTERNAL_PURCHASE_ORDER table into the AVYX EXTERNAL_PURCHASE_ORDER table for HAA
MAPPING.NAME: m_EXT_PUR_ORD_HAA

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF.PLANT_CD as PLANT_CD, EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF.EXTERNAL_PLANT as EXTERNAL_PLANT FROM EXTERNAL_PLANT_XREF

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Acts as a safe expression before target to avoid data type discrepancy
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_EXT_PURC_ORD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on PACK to get PACKAGE_QTY
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_PACK

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ltrim(CODES_TABLE.CODE) as CODE, CODES_TABLE.LONG_DESCRIPTION as LONG_DESCRIPTION FROM CODES_TABLE where CODES_TABLE.CATEGORY= 'DDR'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Joining the table External_purchase_order with SKU_master using ITEM_ID
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_EXTERNAL_PUR_ORDER_SKU_MAST

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT a.as_of_date, a.order_source, a.order_type, a.order_create_date, a.order_number, a.order_line_number, a.order_status, a.sku, a.item_id, a.facility_code, a.facility_id, a.fg_order_qty, a.fg_uom, a.business_id_ref, a.order_ref_1, a.order_ref_2, a.demand_driver, a.exit_factory_date, a.dc_due_date, a.contact_name, a.planner_name, a.transportation_mode, a.port_of_loading, a.delivery_terms, a.payment_method, a.payment_terms, a.season_year, a.season_name, AMENDMENT_NUMBER FROM external_purchase_order a where a.item_id is not null and a.order_source = $$CUSTOMER_CD and a.order_type = 'PO' and a.order_status = '1' and a.fg_order_qty > 0 -- and a.order_create_date > to_date($$CREATE_DATE,'DD-MON-YYYY') and a.as_of_date =(select max(b.as_of_date) from external_purchase_order b where b.item_id is not null and b.order_source = $$CUSTOMER_CD and b.order_type = 'PO' and b.order_status = '1' and b.fg_order_qty > 0 -- and b.order_create_date > to_date($$CREATE_DATE,'DD-MON-YYYY') )

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on STYLE to get PACK_CD
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_STYLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STYLE.PACK_CD as PACK_CD, STYLE.STYLE_CD as STYLE_CD FROM STYLE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Used for calculating current date begin date and Expression to calculate QTY field
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_CURRENT_WK_BEG_DATE_QTY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT b.ITEM_ID, b.SELLING_STYLE_CD, b.SELLING_COLOR_CD, b.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, b.SELLING_SIZE_CD, b.SELLING_REVISION_NO, b.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_MASTER b
